1. Get All Movies
Method: GET
URL: http://localhost/API/index.php/api/movies
2. Get Movie by ID
Method: GET
URL: http://localhost/API/index.php/api/movies/1
3. Create Movie
Method: POST
URL: http://localhost/API/index.php/api/movies
Headers: Content-Type: application/json
Body:
{
  "title": "Spider-Man: No Way Home",
  "description": "Peter Parker seeks help...",
  "duration": 148,
  "genre": "Action",
  "release_date": "2021-12-17"
}
4. Update Movie
Method: PUT
URL: http://localhost/API/index.php/api/movies/1
Headers: Content-Type: application/json
Body:
{
  "title": "Spider-Man: No Way Home (Updated)",
  "description": "Updated description",
  "duration": 150,
  "genre": "Action"
}
5. Delete Movie
Method: DELETE
URL: http://localhost/API/index.php/api/movies/1
ðŸŽ­ SHOWTIMES ENDPOINTS
1. Get All Showtimes
Method: GET
URL: http://localhost/API/index.php/api/showtimes
2. Get Showtimes by Movie
Method: GET
URL: http://localhost/API/index.php/api/showtimes?movie_id=1
3. Get Showtime by ID
Method: GET
URL: http://localhost/API/index.php/api/showtimes/1
4. Create Showtime
Method: POST
URL: http://localhost/API/index.php/api/showtimes
Headers: Content-Type: application/json
Body:
{
  "movie_id": 1,
  "show_date": "2024-01-20",
  "show_time": "16:00:00",
  "theater": "Cinema 2",
  "price": 45000.00
}
5. Update Showtime
Method: PUT
URL: http://localhost/API/index.php/api/showtimes/1
Headers: Content-Type: application/json
Body:
{
  "movie_id": 1,
  "show_date": "2024-01-20",
  "show_time": "18:00:00",
  "theater": "Cinema 2",
  "price": 50000.00
}
6. Delete Showtime
Method: DELETE
URL: http://localhost/API/index.php/api/showtimes/1
ðŸŽ« BOOKINGS ENDPOINTS
1. Get All Bookings
Method: GET
URL: http://localhost/API/index.php/api/bookings
2. Get Bookings by User
Method: GET
URL: http://localhost/API/index.php/api/bookings?user_id=1
3. Get Booking by ID
Method: GET
URL: http://localhost/API/index.php/api/bookings/1
4. Create Booking
Method: POST
URL: http://localhost/API/index.php/api/bookings
Headers: Content-Type: application/json
Body:
{
  "user_id": 1,
  "showtime_id": 1,
  "seats_booked": 2
}
5. Update Booking
Method: PUT
URL: http://localhost/API/index.php/api/bookings/1
Headers: Content-Type: application/json
Body:
{
  "user_id": 1,
  "showtime_id": 1,
  "seats_booked": 3
}
6. Cancel Booking
Method: DELETE
URL: http://localhost/API/index.php/api/bookings/1
ðŸ‘¥ USERS ENDPOINTS
1. Get All Users
Method: GET
URL: http://localhost/API/index.php/api/users
2. Get User by ID
Method: GET
URL: http://localhost/API/index.php/api/users/1
3. Create User
Method: POST
URL: http://localhost/API/index.php/api/users
Headers: Content-Type: application/json
Body:
{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "phone": "08123456789"
}
4. Update User
Method: PUT
URL: http://localhost/API/index.php/api/users/1
Headers: Content-Type: application/json
Body:
{
  "name": "John Doe Updated",
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "phone": "08123456789"
}
5. Delete User
Method: DELETE
URL: http://localhost/API/index.php/api/users/1